											<SHORT-NAME>I2cClockConfiguration</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Reference to a McuClockReferencePoint which is used to calculate the baudrate settings for transmissions on a hardware unit.

Note: If this parameter is set the clock is derived from the MCU.</L-2>
											</DESC>
