											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Reference to the configured DEM event to report "Addressing failure".

Note: "Addressing failure" occurs in case a NACK response is detected and the corresponding sequence is configured to handle NACK as error. </L-2>
											</DESC>
											<LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>1</LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>
											<UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>1</UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>
