											<SHORT-NAME>I2C_E_ARBITRATION_FAILURE</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Reference to the configured DEM event to report "Arbitration failure".

Note: "Arbitration failure" occurs in case the master loses arbitration. This usually happens if the SDA is stuck low.</L-2>
											</DESC>
											<LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>1</LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>
											<UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>1</UPPER-MULTIPLICITY>
